This is where the "ui adapter" bits go for the various views.  Each view
gets
 - a class derived from ViewHandler, which contains the view and associated controller
   logic
 - a class derived from envisage.Plugin:
   a Envisage service plugin wrapping the op

This is also where sphinx goes to look for the user manual's documentation
for each view.  The actual "view" classes are in workflow.views. 
For more details, see docs/dev_manual/guides/new_modules.rst.